  <h1>Account Deletion – YourAppName</h1>

  <p>If you would like to delete your account and all related data, please follow the instructions below.</p>

  <h2>How to Request Account Deletion</h2>
  <p>Please send an email to <strong>your-email@example.com</strong> with the subject line <strong>"Account Deletion Request"</strong>.</p>
  <p>Include the following information to help us identify your account:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Your registered email address</li>
    <li>Any other information related to your account (optional)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data That Will Be Deleted</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Your user profile</li>
    <li>Authentication data (Firebase Auth)</li>
    <li>Saved learning progress and app data</li>
    <li>Saved words or learning history</li>
    <li>Analytics data linked to your account</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Data That May Be Retained</h2>
  <p>Some data may be retained for legal, security, or fraud-prevention purposes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Anonymous analytics data (cannot identify you)</li>
    <li>Crash logs (cannot identify you)</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Retention Period</h2>
  <p>Any retained anonymous data is kept for up to 12 months, after which it will be permanently deleted.</p>

  <p>If you have any questions regarding your account or data deletion, please contact us at <strong>your-email@example.com</strong>.</p>
